episode_event_sinnoh_elitefour/4001_1001:
Yes, it appears so. None of you have changed
a bit.
Right! Nice to see you on Pasio!

Ahaha! Everyone looks happy and healthy. This old
lady can’t help but smile.

Remember, here on Pasio, we’re just challengers.
Don’t get overconfident!
Of course not! I’ll be sure to stay focused!

I should be able to observe strategies and battling
techniques from various other cultures, so at least
I’m unlikely to get bored here.
Wow, Lucian! I see you’re as confident as ever!
Yes, of course. It wouldn’t do for me to lose.

Not to one particular person who’s likely to be
here, that is.
I assume you all feel the same?
Well, I still need to train more.

I plan to find other Bug-type Trainers and train
up together!

I think that’s a good idea. I hope I’m able to find
some interesting books while I’m here as well.

So anyway, I think that’s enough for our little
get-together...
Let’s hurry up and meet the folks of Pasio!
